  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Human Resource Officer / Senior Officer (Foreign Bank)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Manage the whole employee’s life-cycle from on-boarding to off-boarding.</li>\n  <li>Be the first point of contact for employees enquiry on HR policies, employment terms and conditions as well as company benefit.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in the following domains such as full recruitment, talent management, performance appraisal, compensation and benefit, strategic development and more.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for the administering of payroll function which includes claims, overtime payments, bonus and monthly salary.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance of the HR policies and processes.</li>\n  <li>Manage end to end process for all applicants and renewal of work passes and escalate any outstanding issues.</li>\n  <li>Data maintenance in relation to employee information and aligning with the best HR practices and policies.</li>\n  <li>Support internal and external audits, manpower report, government survey and more.</li>\n  <li>Any other tasks or duties assigned by Head of Department or Company from time to time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Skills and Experience required</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s Degree in human resource management, business management or related disciplines.</li>\n  <li>Possess at least 3 to 5 years of relevant experience in Human Resource Management.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in Banking &amp; finance is preferred.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently under minimal supervision.</li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal skills to liaise with multiple stakeholders across various departments.</li>\n  <li>Resourceful and self-driven with a strong sense of urgency to meet deadline.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under pressure.</li>\n  <li>Understanding of HR policies and legislation will be an added advantage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates please email resume in <strong>MS Word format</strong> to <strong>recruit@waterstone.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Please state your last drawn and expected package, relevant skill sets and the position you are applying for.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Resumes collected will be kept in strict confidence and used for recruitment purposes only.</p>",
